The project is an implementation of a frontend design of a QR-Code. I used CSS and HTML. A live site can be found here: https://yarnileach2005-code.github.io/qr-code-frontend-mentor/
In this Project I relearned the basic elements of html and css.
The Project brief can be found here: https://www.frontendmentor.io/challenges/qr-code-component-iux_sIO_H

Implemented CSS based on Figma file. Decided against implementing with Flexbox or Grid because it was only one object.



